Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:20.35,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,È un maschio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.07,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Allora userò il Proiettile di Pietra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:28.65,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,In quanto maschio capisco come ti senti, però...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:29.69,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Scusa, amico!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.49,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Bene, ora posso aiutare Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:34.93,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Noir, guarda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:48.81,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Un B-Big Rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:53.89,Text_Box_Header,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(362,1)\pos(143.333,215)\an2}Big Rabbit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:53.89,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Livello 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.86,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sta' indietro, Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:59.03,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Non ti intromettere. \NMe ne occuperò da sola.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:00.40,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ma perché?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.28,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Perché...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:06.64,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Se compi tu la missione, \Nquella ragazza ti starà di nuovo addosso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.66,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,È veloce nonostante la stazza!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:15.41,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Ma Emma è ancora più veloce!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.33,0:14:22.80,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,È come una farfalla che danza nel vento.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:25.67,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Sei troppo lento.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:29.96,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Bene, facciamola finita!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:32.12,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Colpo di Vento!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.60,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,I-Incredibile!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.39,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Ancora uno!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.51,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Ha saltato?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:10.51,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,A-Appena in tempo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:17.14,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Emma! Da questa parte!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:23.95,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fermiamoci un attimo qui per riordinare le idee.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:27.29,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Verrà presto a cercarci con tutta probabilità.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:29.62,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Dobbiamo capire come affrontarlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:31.90,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Perché non sono riuscita a sconfiggerlo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:33.78,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Continuavo a menar fendenti...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:37.79,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Forse la sua pelle era troppo spessa \Ne non riuscivi a raggiungere i punti vitali.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:41.24,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Sono troppo debole...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.21,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Emma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.80,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Questa cosa l'ha buttata davvero giù.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:48.13,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Dev'esserci qualcosa che posso fare.
