Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:05.58,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Ci siamo! Ho avuto uno sconto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:07.69,Text_Box_Text,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(358,1)\q2\4a&H44&\shad2\pos(385,228)}LP necessari:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.27,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Un attimo però...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.29,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Al momento dispongo di 700 LP.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:13.82,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Se ne usassi 500 subito, \Npotrebbe essere un bel problema.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:17.97,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ascolta...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:22.53,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,io potrei farti diventare più forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:23.99,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,D-Davvero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:27.69,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sì, ma ho bisogno di qualcosa in cambio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:30.72,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,S-Se mi aiuterà a sconfiggere quel coniglio, \Nfarò qualsiasi cosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:31.67,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Va bene, allora...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:33.98,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,posso mordicchiarti l'orecchio?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:38.17,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,T-Ti prometto che faccio piano...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:39.68,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Non ti va?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:47.01,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,D-D'accordo. Fammi tutto ciò che vuoi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:48.65,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Emma...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:54.57,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Non trattenerti!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:56.03,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Non lo farò!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:05.83,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... non sapevo che le orecchie\N fossero così morbide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:18.93,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Noir... non hai ancora finito?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.38,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Forse le sue sono particolarmente sensibili.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:23.32,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Siamo amici da sempre
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:25.94,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,ma immagino ci siano ancora molte cose \Nche non so di lei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:36.30,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.29,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Ci ha trovati!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:49.63,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Presto... Devo sbrigarmi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.17,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Mi servono quei LP!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:01.51,Text_Box_Header,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(442,1)\an7\3c&H262317&\pos(48,32)}Noir Stardia
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:01.20,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Ho fatto il pieno di LP!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:03.47,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Ora, per potenziare l'abilità di Emma—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:23.51,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Proiettile di Pietra 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:26.16,Main,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Nulla è impossibile se si usa la testa, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:27.66,Main,Emma,0000,0000,0000,,Noir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:31.28,Italics,Noir,0000,0000,0000,,Ora userò Modifica per migliorare l'abilità di Emma!
